---
import SectionHeading from "../reuseable/SectionHeading.astro";
import Button from "../reuseable/Button.astro";
---

<SectionHeading title="Services I offer." />
<div class="flex gap-x-9">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-3 w-1/2">
        <h3 class="font-bold">
            <span class="highlight">Your needs, your solution</span>
        </h3>
        <p>Whether you need a new website, a custom software solution for your business or a project administrator, I’ll cover it all. With over 5 years of experience in software development and project management I build software that covers all your needs.</p>
        <ul class="list-[square] list-inside marker:text-primary">
            <li>I’ll offer you different possible solutions.</li>
            <li>I’ll use modern and fast technology.</li>
            <li>I’ll retain best practices.</li>
            <li>I’ll provide support and administration.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-3 items-center justify-center w-1/2 bg-primary bg-opacity-20 px-9">
        <h3 class="text-accent text-black text-5xl text-center">Want a free consultation?</h3>
        <Button href="/contact" title="Contact Me"></Button>
    </div>
</div>
